headline: Garmin’s CEO Made His Company an Electronics Leader. Its Stock Has Outrun Apple’s.
summary: Garmin  has spent two decades in the middle of a disruptive storm.  Then its consumer fitness devices were matched by smartwatches.  While other companies have folded under less pressure, Olathe, Kan.–based Garmin has thrived.
